cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SY, cs.RO 

This paper discusses reinforcement learning (RL) and its augmentation with active inference, which is a framework within cognitive and computational neuroscience. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also discusses decision making and exploration-exploitation trade-offs, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.RO (Robotics).
